    <h1>What is An Assignment?</h1>
    <p>
        Assessment for learning rather than assessment of learning’ reflects the
        true spirit of evaluation system at LPU. Innovative and unparalleled
        IT-integrated practices ensure highest level of integrity and transparency
        throughout.Transparency, accountability and impeccable integrity are the
        hallmarks of assessment and evaluation system at LPU. Inclusion of
        automated mechanisms have led to enhanced accuracy and reduced processing
        time. University follows the concept of table marking, wherein the faculty
        evaluates the same question across all answer scripts which helps to bring
        in consistency and fairness in assessments.
    </p>
